<h2>Purpose</h2>
<p>
  Grounds decision
  <a href="/backlog/1868-reconcile-the-always-loaded-memory-index-with-the-harness-co/">#1868</a> under the
  model-usage watch
  <a href="/backlog/1855-model-usage-watch-keep-claude-s-use-of-the-agent-system-effi/">#1855</a> — the
  always-loaded memory index sits at ~21.97 KB / 140 lines, at the gate&rsquo;s 22 KB ceiling
  (<code>we:scripts/check-memory.mjs:27</code>), and <a href="/backlog/1864-memory-index-prune-dedup-pass-index-is-at-the-22kb-ceiling/">#1864</a>
